    <description>Microsoft OpenJDK 11 is an open source Java Development Kit build of OpenJDK provided by Microsoft.

## Install Options

Custom install directory:

```
choco install microsoft-openjdk11 --params "'INSTALLDIR=C:\Program Files\OpenJDK'"
```

MSI properties: `INSTALLLEVEL=3 /quiet [INSTALLDIR="C:\your\path"]`
